      "writtenOn": "2020-05-28T13:48:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It looks like this is generating a constructor helper call for an expression of the form:\n\nfloat2x2 x \u003d ...;\nfloat2x2 m \u003d float2x2(x); \n\nIs that really needed? You can\u0027t construct a matrix from another matrix of identical dimensions?",
